mens known, claimed or assumed to be part of the type series of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Meyer, AB" authorityYear="1884" box="[854,1124,990,1014]" class="Aves" family="Psittacidae" genus="Geoffroyus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Psittaciformes" pageId="13" pageNumber="464" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="timorlaoensis">
<emphasis box="[854,1124,990,1014]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="464">Geoffroyus timorlaoënsis</emphasis>
